author: Rafael Castro
description:
A couple of years ago when I began to explore data science in-depth, I explored various AI/ DL/ ML applications, and at that moment I decided that once my knowledge and expertise in artificial intelligence had been consolidated, I was going to investigate practice applications in the field of autonomous systems...

... Finally, I have completed the last piece in my training that has allowed me to lay the foundations in an exciting specialization, learning about deep learning applications, sensors, state of the art of computer vision, robotics, etc.

Looking back at the number of experiences accumulated through all the projects, it is undoubtedly gratifying, the adventure is just beginning, but I am sure that it is the starting point to continue growing professionally by holistically applying all the knowledge and experience acquired.

Many thanks to my teachers, mentors, colleagues, partners, #Udacity, and Applaudo Studios, for the opportunity to offer the world significant improvements through the application of our work and knowledge...

author: Rodrigo Morales
description:
Friends, I've been working at Applaudo Studios for a few months now and I can confidently say it has been an outstanding experience, but I'm not writing this to talk about me or my experience, I'm writing this as an invitation that can change your professional life, because this is what this opportunity is.

Often, as new professionals we are asked to have 1 or 2 years of experience to get a job, in turn, to get those years of experience you need a job. And so the wheel goes on...

Applaudo Studios has changed that paradigm, the trainee program allows us, new developers, to build our skill set in a specific technology, to enter the workforce as competent software engineers and develop exciting projects. Here you will grow, you will learn, you will meet amazing developers and make friends out of these bright minds. In time, you will become the developer you dream to be.

Join us and let's start writing #CodeThatChangesLives

description:
Se oggi non scrivessi della vincita di ieri, qui in azienda inizierebbero a togliermi il saluto. Ed avrebbero ragione: il premio ‚ÄúIl mio prodotto del cuore‚Äù. √® qualcosa di speciale perch√® i vincitori sono decretati dai voti del ‚ÄúRe Cliente‚Äù, ossia, dai consumatori che hanno acquistato e provato i prodotti in gara. Insomma: i clienti ci premiano.

Cosa vogliamo di pi√π?

Nel resto d‚ÄôEuropa questa indagine di mercato, che finisce con l'assegnazione del premio, si chiama ‚ÄúBest Product of the Year‚Äù, ma noi italiani siamo degli inguaribili romanticoni: per questo in Italia si chiama ‚ÄúIl mio prodotto del cuore‚Äù.

Ringrazio pubblicamente lo Studio Orlandini (bravissima Beatrice Orlandini!) e Largo Consumo, che nonostante le grandi difficolt√† di quest‚Äôanno non hanno rinunciato a questa iniziativa, mobilitando una macchina pazzesca fatta di marchi, prodotti e spietati clienti, messa in moto completamente on line (premiazione compresa).

Ancora una volta applaudo gli affiliati 101CAFFE' Italia‚Äô, che hanno fatto conoscere questo caff√® cos√¨ speciale a partire dal suo nome (Gran Milano) ed alla mia squadra, di cui in questa foto si vede una parziale ma significativa rappresentanza, a maggioranza femminile (e per questo funziona alla grande).
